          "subtype": "message",
          "text": "Perfect! I've completed the impact analysis for `ModelAdmin.get_list_filter()`. Here's a summary of my findings:\n\n## Impact Analysis Summary\n\nI found **5 files** that reference `get_list_filter`:\n\n### Code Files:\n1. **django/contrib/admin/options.py**\n   - Definition: `def get_list_filter(self, request)` at line 1110\n   - Callers: Lines 498 and 863 where the method is invoked\n\n2. **tests/admin_changelist/admin.py**\n   - Override in `DynamicListFilterChildAdmin` class\n   - Calls `super().get_list_filter(request)`\n\n3. **tests/modeladmin/tests.py**\n   - Override in test class `ConcertAdmin`\n   - Uses method to customize filters based on request\n\n### Documentation Files:\n4. **docs/ref/contrib/admin/index.txt**\n   - Method documentation and references\n\n5. **docs/releases/1.5.txt**\n   - Release notes mentioning the method introduction\n\n## Impact of Signature Change:\nAny change to the signature of `get_list_filter()` would require:\n- Updating the 2 internal callers in the main implementation\n- Updating both test overrides to match the new signature\n- Updating documentation/release notes to reflect the changes\n\nThe `/workspace/submission.json` file has been created with all affected file paths.",
